  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a wok over high heat. Add garlic and ginger, sauté until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Add the sliced chicken and stir‑fry until it turns white, about 3–4 minutes.",
    "Add broccoli florets and bell pepper, stir‑fry for 2 minutes until crisp‑tender.",
    "Stir in fermented bean paste, soy sauce, oyster sauce, and water. Bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the grated Gruyère cheese, stirring until it melts and the sauce thickens, about 2–3 minutes.",
    "Finish with lime juice, season with salt and pepper to taste, and stir for 30 seconds.",
    "Remove from heat, let rest for 2 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Serve hot or let cool and portion into containers for meal prep."
